com.footm.informationservice.api

Class PlayerSkills

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.footm.informationservice.api.PlayerSkills

  • public class PlayerSkills
extends Object
    The class PlayerSkills is a JavaBean objects used to serialize and deserialize JSON request and response object by Jackson. This object contains all skills(Skills) of a player
    Author:
    Rinor Sefa, Lundrim Azemi
